## üß† Knowledge Base (meh)

This project uses **meh** as a knowledge base for AI. You have access to MCP tools.

### Session Workflow

#### 1. START - at the beginning of session
```
meh_get_notifications()      # check what changed
meh_browse("@")              # see structure
meh_get_fact("@readme")      # read onboarding (if exists)
```

#### 2. WORK - during task
```
meh_search("topic")          # BEFORE answering - search if knowledge exists
meh_add("@path", "content")  # document discoveries
```

#### 3. END - after finishing
```
meh_ack_notifications(["*"]) # acknowledge read notifications
```

### Available Tools

| Tool | When to use |
|------|-------------|
| `meh_search` | Search knowledge BEFORE answering |
| `meh_browse` | Browse path structure |
| `meh_get_fact` | Get full fact content |
| `meh_add` | Add new knowledge |
| `meh_correct` | Correct an incorrect fact |
| `meh_extend` | Extend existing fact |
| `meh_deprecate` | Mark fact as outdated |
| `meh_get_notifications` | Check KB changes |
| `meh_ack_notifications` | Acknowledge read |
| `meh_subscribe` | Filter notifications |

### Path Conventions

```
@docs/           - documentation
@bugs/           - found bugs
@todo/           - tasks to do
@decisions/      - architectural decisions
@board/          - dashboards and status
```

